data.description: Welcome to your new oasis at 10440 Orange Blossom Ln in Seminole, Florida! This charming and inviting single-family residence is nestled in the serene Blossom Lake Village. Featuring a robust solid block construction, this home boasts 3 cozy bedrooms, 2 well-appointed bathrooms, a spacious 2-car garage, and a delightful screened-in saltwater pool, all complemented by a fully fenced backyard.  As you arrive, a spacious driveway welcomes you, hinting at the warmth and charm that awaits inside. The exterior's solid block construction, crowned with a durable shingle roof, blends timeless aesthetics with practicality.  Step inside to discover a warm, inviting atmosphere. The central air conditioning offers year-round comfort, while the mix of carpet and tile flooring strikes the perfect balance of style and practicality. Bathed in natural light, the living spaces create an ideal environment for relaxation and entertainment.  At the heart of this home is the kitchen, a perfect blend of functionality and charm, equipped with modern appliances including instant hot water dispenser, dishwasher, microwave, range, and refrigerator, all set off by elegant quartz countertops.  Enjoy the perks of no HOA or CDD fees and no requirement for flood insurance.  Outside, the enclosed patio and screened porch set the stage for sublime outdoor living. The tranquility of the saltwater pool, adorned with LED lights, invites you to craft your own backyard paradise.  Location is key, and this home delivers. A mere 5-minute walk to Blossom Lake Park and Pinellas County Trail, close to shopping, dining, beaches, and Bay Pines Regional VA facility. Just 2 miles from the Gulf's sandy beaches, 8 miles to bustling Downtown Saint Petersburg, and 20 miles to vibrant Downtown Tampa - your highness, you're at the center of it all!  This property is not just a house, it's a lifestyle. Ideal location, beautiful features, and endless possibilities await. Schedule your private tour today and make us a great offer – your Florida dream home is waiting!
